headline: Why Humana Deserves Patience Now: Too Early to Buy, Too Risky to Sell
summary: HUM sits at a crossroads as Medicare Advantage pressures cap near-term upside, but resilience versus peers argues for patience, not panic.

summary: In response to Gov.
